caption: I've been to 3 concerts in the past year so there is no way my mom would pay for another one, and with this opportunity, she won't have to pay for me to meet the boys who saved me. I've been here supporting you for the past 2 years, and I'm going to be here until the end. I've loved watching you boys grow up. I love that the fame hasn't changed you. If I won these tickets I would get to meet my best friend who I was introduced to because of you, and I would be able to meet you guys and thank you for everything you've done for me. My life has been hard the past few months, and getting this opportunity would mean the absolute world to me. You boys saved my life, and being able to thank you for that not over a computer is my biggest goal right now. I love you both so much and I'm always going to be here for you two no matter what❤️ #contest
